    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "このダンスゲームの上級者コース\n意外と簡単だね、愛",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The expert course in this dance game\nis surprisingly easy‚ Ai",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……はぁ……そ、そうですね！　簡単ですよね\n私達、プロですから！　ふぅ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… haa… r-right! It's easy\nWe're‚ professionals! Phew…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "息上がってるけど大丈夫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're out of breath‚ are you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "立て続けに十曲踊っても平気な顔をしてる\n葵さんが特別なんですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Danced ten songs in a row while standing up and still looked fine‚\nAoi-san is special!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "愛はまだまだ無駄な動きが多いんだよ\nだから、疲れるのが早いんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai still has a lot of unnecessary movements\nThat's why you tire so quickly",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "曲に集中してもっと自然に踊ってみるといい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You should focus on the song and dance more naturally",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "し、自然に踊ろうと意識すればするほど\n不自然になっちゃいます～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "More I try to dance naturally‚\nmore unnatural it becomes~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、なぜだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ I wonder why",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.5000012715
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
