      "text": "葵さんは天性のダンサーだからです！\n私なんかに同じことは無理ですよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because Aoi-san is a natural dancer!\nI can't do the same~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.5000012715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.4333346049
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_aoi_01_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことはないよ\n何十曲でも付き合うから、感覚を磨くんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true\nI'll go with you through dozens of songs‚ so sharpen your senses",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4333346049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.2333346049
    },
    {
