      "text": "ごめん、愛の飲み込みが早いから嬉しくて\nつい……やり過ぎたよ。次は愛の好きなゲームをしよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ I was so happy that Ai was learning so fast\n… it was too much. Next‚ let's play Ai's favorite game",
